trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanging" /> cancelable event.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona datos para el evento cancelable <see cref="E:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanging" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs> class contains information for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanging> event.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs> clase contiene información de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModeChanging> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs> class provides access to the display mode that will be applied to the Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartEventArgs> clase proporciona acceso al modo de presentación que se aplicará a lo controles de elementos Web.

trans-unit.source: The display mode is accessed through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs.NewDisplayMode%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: El modo de presentación se accede a través del <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs.NewDisplayMode%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> to apply to a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> que se aplica a un control de elementos Web.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCancelEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the display mode to apply to a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece el modo de presentación que se aplica a un control de elementos Web.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> to apply to a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode" /> que se aplica a un control de elementos Web.
